You will notice the left panel navigation. This navigation panel will allow you to navigate to other editors (bibliographic,OLE Instance: holding or item, or E-Instance) as well as add (click the Green Plus Sign
) and delete (click the White X on Grey
) records.

While viewing a record in the Bib Editor, notice the left panel navigation. This navigation panel will allow you to add (click the Green Plus Sign
) OLE Instance (Holding and Item) and E-Instance records or delete (click the White X on Grey
) Bibliographic Records. While hovering over these icons, a pop-up note will inform the user which icon to click to Add Instance, Add EInstance, or Delete Bib.

